data.description: CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERSA charming 2-story cottage-style home, nestled within the city limits of Blountstown, Florida. Enjoy the prime location, situated within walking distance to grocery shopping and the hospital, ensuring effortless daily errands.The home has been thoughtfully upgraded with a 2019 roof and tankless hot water heater, offering both modern efficiency and durability.
